726825f-a.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 76th Court
726825f-a.text:
Grand Central Parkway, north side, east of about 113th Street.
(Inside the semicircle,at its western edge,formed by 76th Court and
the Parkway). This house is believed to be that of Sarah E. Bolmer.
In 1915 it was occupied by persons conducting a riding Academy.
October 1928.
Eumene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
